Exam 310-203: Upgrade - Sun Certified System Administrator for the Solaris 10 Operating System
</syntaxhighlight>   
 
Solaris 9
  
<syntaxhighlight lang="text">
Exam 310-014: Part I - Sun Certified System Administrator for the Solaris 9 Operating System 
Exam 310-015: Part II - Sun Certified System Administrator for the Solaris 9 Operating System 
Exam 310-016: Upgrade - Sun Certified System Administrator for the Solaris 9 Operating System
